@Node ScreensDisplayed "Screens Displayed"

  Special Screens Displayed
  =========================

    Note: it is unadvisable to use any doors that check the users account for
    details other than thier handle until the Joined screen is displayed

    NoNewAt_All    - if this screen is present, no new users are allowed to join.
    NoNewAt_<Baud> - if this screen is present the user will have to call back
                     using a faster modem.

    GuestLogin     - displayed before the user is asked for account/pw details

    Joined         - displayed when user has joined the system

    OptionMsg_TOP  - displayed before an option message
    OptionMsg_BOT  - displayed after an option message

@EndNode

@Node DoorsCalled "Doors Called"

  Doors Called
  ============

    System Doors:

    SelectLanguage - Called after main options have been selected.
    LinesPerScreen - Called after selectlanguage

    User Doors:

    SENT           - Called after LinesPerScreen

@EndNode

